  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>You favor traditional halfling weapons, so you've learned how to use them more effectively. You have the trained proficiency with the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.UCH4myuFnokGv0vF]{Sling}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.DV4qelKHrviM0O5i]{Halfling Sling Staff}, and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.7tKkkF8eZ4iCLJtp]{Shortsword}.</p>\n<p>You gain access to all uncommon halfling weapons. For the purpose of determining your proficiency, martial halfling weapons are simple weapons and advanced halfling weapons are martial weapons.</p>"
